@NODE "Main" "Z80Simulator Documentation:"
@INDEX "Index"

  @{BOLD "Z80Simulator"} is a program that gives you a visual representation of a
   Z80 microprocessor.  It shows you the Z80 mnemonic that was executed
   & the effects it had on the processor registers (see @{" ScreenShot " LINK "Z80SimWindow.iff/Main"}).
   
   @{" I've " LINK "Author"} tried to make@{BOLD Z80Simulator} a complete Z80 development environment
   (you have to supply your own hardware & Z80 code to view).

   @{" How do I work this? " LINK "Usage"}

   See Also, @{" Index " LINK "Index"}

@ENDNODE

